# Rust build artifacts
**/target/
target/

# WASM build output (deploy + certora prover binaries; rebuilt by `make wasm-artifacts`)
/artifacts/

**/*.rs.bk

# Test fixtures (regenerated by tests; exclude to avoid churn)
**/test_snapshots/

# Certora prover debug output (regenerated on every prover run)
**/.certora_internal/
certora/.prover-run-*.txt
certora/controller/results/*.md

# Fuzz artifacts (mirrors tests/fuzz/.gitignore)
tests/fuzz/corpus/
tests/fuzz/artifacts/
tests/fuzz/coverage/
# cargo-mutants run output (regenerated per invocation)
mutants.out/
mutants.out.old/
**/mutants.out/
**/mutants.out.old/
docs/*
# Keep brainstorming specs tracked even though the rest of docs/ is generated.
!docs/superpowers/
.zed
# Claude Code runtime
.claude/
.antigravitycli
.remember
.playwright-mcp
